      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NEVELE ARMA (4) opened her career in pleasing fashion last start, finishing second and beaten a nose over 1684m at this track. Won't find this any harder and she can go right on with the job. OUR ROBYN HOOD (3) is at the track for the first time. By Always B Miki and hails from the Murray Lindau stable. No excuses from this advantageous draw. Trial winner who looks above average. Has the right credentials to play a major role. MY SWEET MIKI (5) is a two-year-old filly from the Aiden De Campo yard on debut. Showed some ability when a minor placegetter in a recent trial. Finds a nice race so anticipating a bright start to her career. THEMARASSHADOW (7) must be respected after scoring an all of the way last start by a nose at this track over 1684m when sent out at long odds.",
